      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEAR NOT FRENZY (1) was safely held on debut when seventh (24.05) at this track over 400m. Has the inside box this time. Should be much improved and rates a winning chance. SNEAKY MOUSE (2) looks close to another win after finishing third last time (30.49) in a Grade 5 at this track. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Will give a great sight again. RITZA BOB (4) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 4.5 lengths from the winner (30.49). The form from his last run stacks up well. Can measure up this time. KALANI CRUISE (5) is another with top-three prospects.",
